    • Field Detail

      • baseBeans

        protected Map<String,Bean> baseBeans
        ModelSet base beans.

        A Smooks configuration can have multiple that can be wired together in all sorts of ways to create models. This is a Map of these baseBeans. These baseBeans are used (cloned) to create all possible models (with baseBeans all wired together).

      • models

        protected Map<String,Bean> models
        Models.

        Should contain clones of the same baseBeans as in the baseBeans property (above), but with their full graphs expanded i.e. all the bean wirings resolved and wired into parent baseBeans etc.

      • isBindingOnlyConfig

        protected Boolean isBindingOnlyConfig
        Is the associated Smooks instance a binding only configuration.
